Package triple.com

Class Database

java.lang.Object
triple.com.Database
public class Database extends Object
The Database class serves as a mock database for storing various entities such as clients, instructors, articles, programs, feedback, and plans. It handles the storage and management of these entities in static ArrayLists. This class simulates database operations like adding, removing, and retrieving objects.
